                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8899" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0278</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1094 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">健康“味业”社会责任担当能否撑起一片“海天”？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Healthy &quot;flavor industry&quot; social responsibility to assume the role of whether to support a &quot;sea and sky&quot;?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于培友，栾舒月，王晨，宁文红</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佛山市海天调味食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；海天味业；信息披露；社会责任；财务绩效</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG, Haitian Taste, Disclosure, CSR, Financial Performance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球可持续发展的视域下，如何通过ESG及社会责任实践提升可持续发展水平，已成为企业当前发展所面临的重要议题。海天味业，作为中国调味品行业的领军企业，近年来面临了社会责任方面的严峻挑战。本案例以2022年9月末海天味业发生的“添加剂事件”为主线，阐述了近年海天味业在社会责任履行方面出现的问题，以“添加剂事件”致股价、营收双下滑现象，并梳理归纳了其应对社会责任危机时在信息披露、监督体系改进、研发投入加大和供应链完善等方面进行的针对性调整，以及对企业的绩效影响情况。通过本案例旨在引导读者理解企业履行社会责任的相应措施与社会价值，思考如何实现企业价值与社会责任履行之间的动态平衡，并由此为其他上市公司在进行ESG信息披露和社会责任履行时提供相应的参考与借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the perspective of global sustainable development, how to improve the level of sustainable development through ESG and CSR practices has become an important issue for enterprises in their current development. Haitian Taste, as a leader in China&#39;s flavor industry, has faced serious challenges in terms of CSR in recent years. This case focuses on the &quot;additive incident&quot; that happened in Haitian Taste in late September 2022, and describes the problems in Haitian Taste&#39;s fulfillment of CSR in recent years, and summarizes the problems in its response to the CSR crisis in the form of the &quot;additive incident&quot; leading to the phenomenon of a double decline in share price and revenue. It also summarizes the adjustments made in information disclosure, supervision system improvement, R&amp;D investment and supply chain improvement in response to the CSR crisis, as well as the impact on corporate performance. This case aims to guide readers to understand the corresponding measures and social value of corporate CSR fulfillment, to consider how to achieve a dynamic balance between corporate value and CSR fulfillment, and to provide reference for other listed companies in ESG disclosure and CSR fulfillment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任理论；信号传递理论；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
